{"tid":2404650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國、加拿大、德國、澳洲？","createTime":"2021-02-11T23:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T02:07:00.000Z","uid":385838,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27b76d0464cbe5b90cccb7b4fbd5f285857e4125","tid":2404650,"uid":385838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"小弟開咗個YouTube channel，講 <strong><ins>美國政治庇護</ins></strong>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClP87i5mfCGAXxDZUGyYGXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUClP87i5mfCGAXxDZUGyYGXA&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=b503a3dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClP87i5mfCGAXxDZUGyYGXA</a><br />\n<br />\n上年同咗好多香港人合作，大部分都上咗岸了。有啲朋友就仲等緊。<br />\n大家有無啲咩想知？<br />\n不吝賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb6f62bf2bfa60cf06e6a06f6396c17b5fae567","tid":2404650,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T23:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97de06fa8b934cd63de8c0c267b101d3ebb25e54","tid":2404650,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T23:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a192107a9fb3e120ae3be85209983d4b7877e0b","tid":2404650,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60debe418d4e3eface9409224e6000e9aa19932e","tid":2404650,"uid":134059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"Good job 巴打，幫得幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"7117b57289f0cd9844edc38ef997f2501e3a8471","tid":2404650,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"你個隔喇底的確好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736e4cf6ed46e95b3c29d181f5611a9cacf1a79a","tid":2404650,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:24:40.000Z","msg":"你要幫手足就低調D<br />\n擺上黎咪比支那豬玩爛"},{"pid":"3618272422c8a28437dbeca2549d10d7498628eb","tid":2404650,"uid":385838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a192107a9fb3e120ae3be85209983d4b7877e0b","tid":2404650,"uid":162114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"將香港人列入難民配額嘅係《香港避風港法案》，幾日前喺國會又再提交。主要係幫一啲現在<strong>並非</strong>身處美國，而又因基於政治信念、或參加過反對中國/共產黨運動、或<strong><ins>有可能</ins></strong>會收到迫害嘅朋友，可以喺美國全球任何大使館/領事館申請第二類優先難民身份。批准之後，就可以嚟美國。<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，係會容易咗嘅。但係時間上無保證。我認識有人，都係第二類優先，喺原居地（並非香港）等咗3年都未審批到。<br />\n<br />\n而另一個法案《香港人民自由和選擇法案》，就係俾而家已經身在美國，而又有有效簽證嘅香港人（譬如學生簽證）可以獲得臨時保護身份（TPS），可以喺美國居留、工作。<br />\n<br />\n但係TPS係每年由國土安全部審視一次嘅，隨時會取消。<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果香港人有辦法逃出咗香港，嚟到美國的話，申請政治庇護係最有機會成功嘅。<br />\n<br />\n希望解答到您嘅問題。"},{"pid":"abf1ee0c13e07c1acaa9e04b173dd48d66eb7bec","tid":2404650,"uid":385838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60debe418d4e3eface9409224e6000e9aa19932e","tid":2404650,"uid":134059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"Good job 巴打，幫得幾多得幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"呢一年以嚟，向我求救嘅朋友講咗好多故事俾我知，非常心噏&hellip;&hellip;我只能以自己所知，儘量幫佢地。"},{"pid":"468f38f507fe697b4ece316341183dbb2841de8f","tid":2404650,"uid":385838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7117b57289f0cd9844edc38ef997f2501e3a8471","tid":2404650,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"你個隔喇底的確好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"我小學時候嘅無聊笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc54eaaff5c9529bc8bb4eb907e5983ad5ec2dc","tid":2404650,"uid":385838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"736e4cf6ed46e95b3c29d181f5611a9cacf1a79a","tid":2404650,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:24:40.000Z","msg":"你要幫手足就低調D<br />\n擺上黎咪比支那豬玩爛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"我初頭都有咁諗過。好多人都話要 靜靜雞贏。但經過咗呢段時間，我越來越覺得靜靜雞只會帶嚟沉默嘅慘敗，最後連死咗都唔知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n有啲搵我嘅朋友，真係唔知原來有一條路可以咁行。做呢行嘅，九成九都係中國人。香港人（講廣東話嘅）十分少。所以希望多啲有需要嘅人知道。"}]}